an finely optimized tariffs. Overall, we expect small but mutually beneficial trades in which badger gradually accumulates both red and blue from the others, Camel shifts toward more red and fewer blue, and Squid offloads red and perhaps trades blue or green depending on inferred prices, with some proposals being declined when they fail to offer clear surplus to at least one counterpart.",
